# Labrador ELN — Cursor Rules

## Project Identity
- Product name: Labrador ELN
- Repo: github.com/tyoung-4/myfirst-eln (repo name unchanged)
- Local path: ~/labrador-eln
- Deployed on: Railway

## Stack
- Next.js 16 (App Router) + TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS (utility classes only, no custom CSS)
- Prisma ORM + PostgreSQL
- pnpm (never npm or yarn)
- Docker for PostgreSQL in dev only

## Dev Setup
- PostgreSQL runs in Docker: `docker-compose -f docker-compose.dev.yml up -d`
- Next.js runs locally: `pnpm dev`
- Full Docker build is production only

## Naming & Branding
- App name: Labrador ELN
- Search feature is called: Fetch (Cmd+K)
- Dog-themed Easter eggs are intentional — do not remove them
- Turtle progress bar in Active Run is intentional

## Database Rules
- Prisma migrations are ALWAYS additive — never reset, never drop tables
- Always run: `npx prisma migrate dev --name [name]` then `npx prisma generate`
- Never use `prisma migrate reset` without explicit user confirmation
- PostgreSQL only — never revert to SQLite

## Git Conventions
- Always branch before every feature: `git checkout -b feature/[name]`
- No parallel feature branches on the same working tree
- Merge branches sequentially into main
- Commit messages: conventional commits format (feat:, fix:, chore:, etc.)

## Code Conventions
- TypeScript strict mode — no `any` types
- Tailwind utility classes only
- Time format everywhere: 9:00 am / 9:30 am — 30-minute granularity
- Desktop-first UI — mobile deferred to Phase 2
- Dark theme throughout
- Operator is free-text — no auth system yet
- Local file storage only (/uploads) — cloud migration later

## Architecture
- Entry types config: src/config/entryTypes.ts
- Equipment defaults: src/config/equipmentDefaults.ts
- Search config: src/config/searchConfig.ts
- Spec file: spec.md in repo root

## Protocol Data Model (as of migration: protocol-schema-restructure)
- Every step must belong to a section — no orphan steps
- ProtocolSection: has name (required), order, belongs to Protocol
- ProtocolStep: belongs to a section, has stepType (STEP | SUBSTEP)
- Sub-steps point to parent via parentStepId
- estimatedMinutes is nullable Int on each step
- StepType enum: STEP | SUBSTEP

## Navigation
- Top nav: Home, Equipment, Ingestion, Active Runs only
- Protocols, Inventory, Knowledge Hub accessible from Dashboard boxes only

## Out of Scope
- cryo-EM raw data (.mrc files) — lives in cryoSPARC
- Mobile/iPad UI — Phase 2
- Authentication — planned (NextAuth.js), not yet built
- Cloud file storage — planned, not yet built

## On the Horizon
- .eln export format (ELN Consortium standard, RO-Crate-based)
- Run Mode with Pass/Fail/Skip per step
- Reagent library + auto-generated materials lists
- Authentication (NextAuth.js)
- Protocol print/PDF preview mode
- MS proximity labeling data RAG tool
